1.00	Ben_Ottewell	Ben Ottewell	Ben Ottewell is an English singer-songwriter. He is one of the three lead singers of the English indie rock band Gomez. He was the recipient of the Mercury Music Award Prize in 1998, and is well known for his "deep, raspy voice" and "gravelly baritone". Ottewell has recently embarked upon a solo-project, with the debut album Shapes &amp; Shadows.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/da/Ben_Ottewell_at_the_TLA_%28Theater_of_Living_Arts%29_in_Philadelphia.jpg/220px-Ben_Ottewell_at_the_TLA_%28Theater_of_Living_Arts%29_in_Philadelphia.jpg
